wiki.content:
"Outrageous" is the fourth single from American Pop singer Britney Spears' 4th studio album, In The Zone. It was released by Jive on July 13, 2004. It was announced as a single after it was selected as the theme song for the 2004 film Catwoman.
 
 There was originally supposed to be a video, but Britney hurt her knee and had to undergo arthroscopic surgery.
